name: audioError
description: Emitted and executed when audio throws an error.

name: queueEnd
description: Emitted and executed when the music player queue ends.

name: queueStart
description: Emitted and executed when the music player queue starts.

name: trackAdd
description: Emitted and executed when a track is added into the music player.

name: trackEnd
description: Emitted and executed when a track ends.

name: trackPause
description: Emitted and executed when a track is paused.

name: trackResume
description: Emitted and executed when a track is resumed.

name: trackStart
description: Emitted and executed when a track starts playing.
